data.description: Receive grants up to $17,500 through special program. Ask for more details.Elegance, comfort and convenience come together in this delightful 3 bedroom home! Sunny and warm, open concept floorplan greets you with high ceilings! Inviting living room with polished laminate flooring, fireplace and ceiling fan. Modern kitchen with beautiful quartz counter tops, stainless steel appliances, island and pantry lead to your dining room nook and out to the covered patio and fenced yard. Impressive upstairs primary suite offers both soaking tub and walk-in shower with attached, spacious walk-in closet! Superb location offers easy access to Wa-500 and I-205, with shopping, restaurants, grocery stores, and highly rated schools nearby. This home is a must see!  Open House 9/23, 12-2!
